${alignr}$font < $mem/$memmax > -─┘    │    │    │  
${alignr}$font < ${top_mem name 1}  ${top_mem mem 1} > -─┤    │    │  
${alignr}$font < ${top_mem name 2}  ${top_mem mem 2} > -─┤    │    │  
${alignr}$font < ${top_mem name 3}  ${top_mem mem 3} > -─┤    │    │  
